Who We Are

Partnership for a Safe Seattle

The Seattle Police Foundation is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization that raises supplemental funding for the Seattle Police Department. Our supporters are our greatest strength, helping to champion our vision of a healthy police department and a safe Seattle for all who live, work, and play here.
